        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Instead of chain links, this <em>+1 chain shirt</em> is assembled from metal \"leaves\" that each resemble a small blade.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">1</span> Interact</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You pull a link from the armor, which transforms into a <em>+1 striking @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Dagger]</em>. The dagger disappears and reappears as a link in the armor after you Strike with it, or at the end of this turn if you don't make a Strike. You can Activate the blade byrnie in place of an Interact action to draw a weapon for abilities such as the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Quick Draw] feat.</p>\n<p>Upgrading the runes on the blade byrnie makes the daggers pulled from it more powerful. The daggers have a <em>+2 weapon potency</em> rune if the armor has a <em>+2 armor potency</em> rune, or a <em>+3 weapon potency</em> rune if the armor has a <em>+3 armor potency</em> rune.</p>"
